body:
@oscarriddle : CUDA may not be available on many mobile devices.  
In short term TFLite will support acceleration using OpenGL and other drivers that can target GPU. 

Technically, it is certainly possible to write a [delegate](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/delegates) that uses CUDA for acceleration.
